deploy to a container
=====================
doing the above steps you will set the java,git,maven variables...
go to plugins=>available plugins =>search deploy to container and install it
now move to manage jenkins=>credentails=>system=>globalcredentails=>add credentails=>
		=>set username:=> tomcatscript
	              password:=>tomcatscriptpwd
                      id:=>tomcatscript
description:credentails to connect to remote tomcat and to be able to deploy applications
navigate to the deplotocontainer job=>add postbuild action =>war/ear files=>
                    war/ear=>  target/helloworld.war
                    contextpath=>/helloworld
                    add tomcattomcat container
